race.comment: AVISWOOD (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (22.72) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. SALMON SPRAY (4) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (26.21) in a Grade 5 at this track. Worth following up. PAW HULL (8) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Missed the frame latest (24.05) when fourth over 410m at Horsham in a Grade 5. Can feature with the right run. NOLAN BALE (2) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at Geelong (23.35) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.
